Package: LBDiscoverAnalysis
Title: Co-occurrence Discovery Models and Visualization for Biomedical LBD
Version: 0.1.0.9000
Date: 2025-05-14
Authors@R: 
    person("Chao Liu", email = "chaoliu@cedarville.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9979-8272"))
Description: Analysis-focused components for literature-based discovery in
    biomedical research. Provides co-occurrence analysis utilities,
    discovery models (ABC, AnC, LSI, BITOLA-style methods), validation
    workflows, and visualization/reporting functions. The package depends
    on 'LBDiscoverData' for article retrieval, preprocessing, and entity
    extraction.
License: GPL-3
URL: https://github.com/chaoliu-cl/LBDiscover, https://liu-chao.site/LBDiscoverAnalysis/
BugReports: https://github.com/chaoliu-cl/LBDiscover/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
